<li class="comment byuser comment-author-bravenewclimate bypostauthor odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-114361">
<div id="div-comment-114361">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/66d42919adcf3f34221f7a7c94745cfe?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://bravenewclimate.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Barry Brook</a></strong>, on <a href="#comment-114361" title="">13 March 2011 at 10:47 PM</a> said:		</span>
