<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-114477">
<div id="div-comment-114477">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e17086c4c3760aecfb7ae4af55274035?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn">valwayne</strong>, on <a href="#comment-114477" title="">14 March 2011 at 7:28 AM</a> said:		</span>
