	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5b4c0ebd375b05a259e0c4906a23487b?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn">R. L. Citerley, P.E.</strong>, on <a href="#comment-114555" title="">14 March 2011 at 10:25 AM</a> said:		</span>
