	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/3ebc748dbbbfd6a20ce1794b14229563?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://www.zealous.co' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Guy Armitage</a></strong>, on <a href="#comment-114760" title="">14 March 2011 at 5:09 PM</a> said:		</span>
