<li class="pingback odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-114809">
<div id="div-comment-114809">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://addle.biz/blog/?p=11411' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>&#8220;Fukushima Nuclear Accident – a simple and accurate explanation&#8221; and related posts | The news blog</a></strong>, on <a href="#comment-114809" title="">14 March 2011 at 6:24 PM</a> said:		</span>
			</div>

	<p>[...] post by Top Stories &#8211; Google Blog Search and software by Elliott Back    This entry was posted in Uncategorized. Bookmark the permalink.    [...]</p>

	<div class="reply">
