	<p>Jason; the 2nd explosion at Fukushima Unit 3 was planned. They didn&#8217;t know exactly when it will happen, but the Japanese Government thru Mr Edano, Chief Cabinet Secretary has already announced this explosion yesterday to win public confidence. This is just a hydrogen detonation, an announcement was made yesterday so that the public does not speculate along the lines of that it could be a nuclear chain reaction explosion.</p>
<p>They announced that the explosion will happen today. But they didn&#8217;t know exactly when.</p>

