	<p>[...] same article appears here <a href="http://bravenewclimate.com/2011/03/13/fukushima-simple-explanation/ and" rel="nofollow">http://bravenewclimate.com/2011/03/13/fukushima-simple-explanation/ and</a> includes [...]</p>

