<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-115162">
<div id="div-comment-115162">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/dd4f00fa300897e08528a9eefa02c306?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn">Jeffrey</strong>, on <a href="#comment-115162" title="">15 March 2011 at 4:22 AM</a> said:		</span>
