	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5c68aae2070212b92dfe372b2b036df5?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn">Jen</strong>, on <a href="#comment-117236" title="">17 March 2011 at 1:49 PM</a> said:		</span>
