<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-118046">
<div id="div-comment-118046">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ef0ec6c861c8ea39dab7618232682819?s=32&amp;d=retro' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' /></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn">Chris Harries</strong>, on <a href="#comment-118046" title="">18 March 2011 at 6:08 PM</a> said:		</span>
