	<p>To add to Snord&#8217;s entry, the theory of plate tectonics was not fully appreciated until the 1960s – even Albert Einstein was sceptical of the theory in the early 1950s.</p>
<p>The Fukushima facility was built in 1971.</p>
<p>What does this mean? Well perhaps that we could excuse those who built the Fukushima plant back then, but what&#8217;s around the corner that we don&#8217;t know about yet?</p>

