<li class="pingback odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-119010">
<div id="div-comment-119010">
	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<div class="avatar"></div>		<span class="comment-author vcard"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://returnofking2003.wordpress.com/2011/03/20/%e6%84%9a%e3%81%ae%e9%aa%a8%e9%a0%82%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8d%e7%a2%ba%e3%81%8b%e3%81%aa%e6%83%85%e5%a0%b1%e3%81%ab%e6%8c%af%e3%82%8a%e5%9b%9e%e3%81%95%e3%82%' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>愚の骨頂：不確かな情報に振り回される | TOUCHBASE</a></strong>, on <a href="#comment-119010" title="">20 March 2011 at 1:47 PM</a> said:		</span>
